# Frontend standards

- Vite + React + TypeScript + Tailwind. No heavy UI kit.
- Server state via TanStack Query; UI state via `useState`/`useReducer`.
- Consume only the FastAPI contract in `references/design/05-frontend.md` (`:8000`).
- Real-time via SSE on `/api/runs/{id}/events`; poll `/api/runs/{id}` every 2s as fallback.
- Failed asset tiles must render a graceful "generation failed" card, never crash the board.
- No secrets in the frontend. The gallery talks only to the local FastAPI backend.
- Lint: `eslint` + `prettier` must pass. No `any` without a comment explaining why.
